text: Facelina goslingii is a species of sea slug, an aeolid nudibranch, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Facelinidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Facelina goslingii A. E. Verrill, 1901. Accessed on 2018-02-17. ==Distribution== This species was described from Bermuda. ==References== Category:Facelinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1901
title: Facelina goslingii
